  <V n="entry_text_description" t="enabled">
    <T n="enabled">0x4811D770<!--String: "In Wanderwood Wilds, the Melody of the Geyser is a legendary tune known to coax the geyser into a fiery display. The key lies in striking the unique spherical rocks nearby, each tap releasing a resonant note. This harmonious frequency awakens the geyser, causing lava to erupt and butterflies to appear, echoing the Plumbirds' magical legacy."--></T>
